<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="201" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,373,649]" pageId="5" pageNumber="201">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,587,613]" pageId="5" pageNumber="201">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species is known only from the male. It can be distinguished from congeners by the hypandrium narrowed at apex, medially with a broad ridge.
</paragraph>
